   299	     * @dev Transfer all of this strategy's assets to a new one, without any losses.
   300	     * 1. This strategy flashloans it's current aave debt from balancer, pays it, and transfers it's collateral to the
   301	     * new strategy.
   302	     * 2. This strategy calls `createAaveDebt` on the new strategy, such that new strategy has the same aave debt as
   303	     * this strategy did before the upgrade.
